《'''一級危險'''》（{{lang-en|'''''Gimme Danger'''''}}）是一部2016年[[美國|美國]][[紀錄片|紀錄片]]，由[[吉姆·賈木許|吉姆·賈木許]]執導和擔任編劇。該片於[[第69屆坎城影展|第69屆坎城影展]]上的午夜放映首映<ref name="IW">{{cite web |url=http://www.indiewire.com/article/cannes-live-stream-2016-film-festival-lineup-list |title=2016 Cannes Film Festival Announces Lineup |accessdate=2016-04-15 |work=IndieWire |archive-date=2016-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160505030458/http://www.indiewire.com/article/cannes-live-stream-2016-film-festival-lineup-list |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="VarCannes">{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2016/film/festivals/cannes-film-festival-official-selection-lineup-2016-1201753269/ |title=Cannes 2016: Film Festival Unveils Official Selection Lineup |accessdate=2016-04-15 |work=Variety |archive-date=2016-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160423225526/http://variety.com/2016/film/festivals/cannes-film-festival-official-selection-lineup-2016-1201753269/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並定於2016年10月28日在美國上映。

== 劇情 ==
主要敘述美國[[丑角合唱團|丑角合唱團]]在輝煌時期的傳奇故事。

== 發行 ==
2016年4月，{{le|亞馬遜影業|Amazon Studios}}獲得了該紀錄片的美國發行權<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.screendaily.com/news/distribution/amazon-studios-woos-cinemacon/5102627.article|title=Amazon Studios woos CinemaCon|website=[[Screen_Daily|Screen Daily]]|first=Jermey|last=Kay|date=2016-04-14|accessdate=2016-07-31|archive-date=2020-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200727015737/https://www.screendaily.com/news/distribution/amazon-studios-woos-cinemacon/5102627.article|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並與{{le|Magnolia Pictures}}共同發行本片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.magpictures.com/profile.aspx?id=fc94b81f-1f90-480b-9f14-0a065cd5e46b|title=Gimme Danger|website=[[Magnolia_Pictures|Magnolia Pictures]]|accessdate=2016-07-31|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160808072258/http://www.magpictures.com/profile.aspx?id=fc94b81f-1f90-480b-9f14-0a065cd5e46b|archivedate=2016-08-08}}</ref>。本片於2016年5月19日在[[第69屆坎城影展|第69屆坎城影展]]上作全球首映<ref name="VarCannes">{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2016/film/festivals/cannes-film-festival-official-selection-lineup-2016-1201753269/ |title=Cannes 2016: Film Festival Unveils Official Selection Lineup |accessdate=2016-04-15 |work=Variety}}</ref>。2016年9月8日，本片也於[[2016年多倫多國際影展|多倫多國際影展]]上放映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/08/09/TIFF-2016-leonardo-dicaprio-documentary|title=Leonardo DiCaprio documentary, Blair Witch sequel headed to TIFF|website=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|first=Joey|last=Nolfi|date=2016-08-09|accessdate=2016-09-14|archive-date=2020-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200604211452/https://ew.com/article/2016/08/09/tiff-2016-leonardo-dicaprio-documentary/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tiff.net/films/gimme-danger/|title=Gimme Danger|website=[[Toronto_International_Film_Festival|Toronto International Film Festival]]|accessdate=2016-09-14|archive-url=https://archive.is/20161027073823/http://www.tiff.net/films/gimme-danger/|archive-date=2016-10-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，以及於2016年10月5日在[[紐約影展|紐約影展]]上展出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/new-york-film-festival-2016-main-slate-1201833076/|title=New York Film Festival Loads 2016 Main Slate With Festival-Circuit Favorites|website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|first=Gordon|last=Cox|date=2016-08-09|accessdate=2016-09-14|archive-date=2016-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821072612/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/new-york-film-festival-2016-main-slate-1201833076/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://filmlinc.org/films/gimme-danger|title=Gimme Danger|website=[[New_York_Film_Festival|New York Film Festival]]|accessdate=2016-09-14|archive-date=2017-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170207013930/https://www.filmlinc.org/films/gimme-danger/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國定於2016年10月28日在戲院上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indiewire.com/2016/09/gimme-danger-images-jim-jarmusch-iggy-pop-the-stooges-documentary-1201725276/|title=‘Gimme Danger’ Exclusive Images: Jim Jarmusch’s New Documentary Recounts The History of The Stooges|website=[[Indiewire.com|Indiewire.com]]|first=Annakeara|last=Stinson|date=2016-09-12|accessdate=2016-09-14|archive-date=2020-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812101244/https://www.indiewire.com/2016/09/gimme-danger-images-jim-jarmusch-iggy-pop-the-stooges-documentary-1201725276/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

